collectionMetadata.name: Sold and Rented HDB Properties and Facilities
collectionMetadata.description: Number of HDB properties/facilities allocated (i.e. sold and rented out), by Financial Year

datasetMetadata.name: Number of Sold and Rented HDB Social Communal Facilities
datasetMetadata.description:
Number of HDB social and communal facilities (e.g. childcare centre, education centre, social function hall) allocated, by Financial Year 

Note: 
Day Activity Centres have been further segmented to Day Activity Centre (Disabled) and Day Activity Centre (Senior Citizens) from FY 2012.

datasetMetadata.name: Number of Sold and Rented HDB Industrial Properties
datasetMetadata.description:
Number of HDB industrial properties allocated (i.e. sold and rented out), by Financial Year 

Note: 
TOL Land refers to land that is not required for immediate development and can be let out for short-term use on Temporary Occupation Licence (TOL).

datasetMetadata.name: Number of Sold and Rented HDB Commercial Properties
datasetMetadata.description: Number of HDB Commercial Properties allocated (i.e. sold and rented out), by Financial Year

datasetMetadata.name: Number of Sold and Rented HDB Residential Units
datasetMetadata.description:
Flats are considered sold only when keys are issued to the applicants. These flats would thus comprise flats booked in the reported financial year and those booked in previous financial years which were under construction. 

Prior to FY2011, data excludes studio apartments and keys issued by private developers under the Design, Build and Sell Scheme. 

Data on rental flats refers to flats under the Public Rental Scheme.
